text: Ðis sant þa land imare to Alderescumbe.
Ærest of langan riple up be Wirtrume on Wlfgedyte.
On deodewoldding lege suðeward of teoþewolding lege adune be dich.
Of þat dich, forðe be Wirtrime on heahstanes quabben, forð be Wirtrime andlang riple at twelf akeres yrðlandes be þe hegewege went on Putelmade.
